  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EndpointSupport, ProtocolDescriptionSupport, Referenceable, DataSupport, com.genesyslab.platform.commons.protocol.runtime.UpdatableProtocolId, ContactServerMessage, Printable, RequestorInfoSupport
    public final class RequestDelete
extends AbstractMessage
    This request is intended for deletion of the contact by its ID.

    Required parameters:
    Name Description
    setContactId(java.lang.String) Unique ID for the Contact to be deleted.

    Related Events:
    Name Description
    EventDelete This event indicates that the contact with the specified ID was deleted.
    EventError Indicates that the request encountered an error.
